message.raw:
* _close_data.py: fix bug where chunk_starts, chunk_ends not
	written for supercontigs with zero present data

	* genomedata_load_data.c: allow other delimiters besides space for
	variableStep and fixedStep, allow wiggle_0 track specification,
	wrap __attribute__((noreturn)) as NORETURN for non-gcc use, add xgetline()
